###
Here you have an ghost application, deploy that on dcos azure using these commands


###

dcos marathon app add ghost.json

####

to check the app go to the public IP. If you don't know the public IP the run this command

az network public-ip list --resource-group devops-azureinternational-test0002-rg01 --query "[?contains(name,'dcos-agent')].[ipAddress]" -o tsv

